{"tid":880370,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵返隻好耐之前嘅遊戲","createTime":"2018-10-28T16:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T06:12:30.000Z","uid":206667,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d0a16704b9da5dbc0ed25c02ffbf62b9f7c4f022","tid":880370,"uid":206667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T16:32:07.000Z","msg":"之前細個成日同呀哥一齊玩，咩平台已經唔記得。係橫向清怪過版game黎嘅，一開波要揀人，之後就間屋著火，要邊走邊打。之後去到中段要打一個boss，佢有把劍，打贏佢而你又揀咗主角玩，你就可以執佢黎用，其他人唔得。我淨係記得咁多，求各位巴打幫幫手，救下我個童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d543278c7601249fd6204c5c95dcd83f084f784","tid":880370,"uid":116530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T16:34:26.000Z","msg":"LF2"},{"pid":"807208a9431d5c67bf0daa6117dd39fffc9d584e","tid":880370,"uid":206667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4d543278c7601249fd6204c5c95dcd83f084f784","tid":880370,"uid":116530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T16:34:26.000Z","msg":"LF2"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T16:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係"},{"pid":"4f2df8d58fb0431e418113374d2a6dd8880e058f","tid":880370,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T16:49:26.000Z","msg":"啲怪係咩樣，現代定古代<br />\n主角用咩武器"},{"pid":"215c5c61d52e57b4111aaf9787745e04e911bb2a","tid":880370,"uid":206667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f2df8d58fb0431e418113374d2a6dd8880e058f","tid":880370,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T16:49:26.000Z","msg":"啲怪係咩樣，現代定古代<br />\n主角用咩武器"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T16:51:28.000Z","msg":"應該係古代，怪就唔記得了，主角係用把好大嘅劍，贏咗中段隻boss就可以換佢把劍(一定要係主角)"},{"pid":"f6ac672c39c721855c0b4a77e6d21e799687be70","tid":880370,"uid":67806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,